INSERT INTO `employers` VALUES (5,'Capgemini','Capgemini_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><strong>Make a start on a challenging, rewarding career</strong></p><p>Capgemini,\r\n one of the world’s foremost providers of consulting, technology and \r\noutsourcing services, enables its clients to transform and perform \r\nthrough technologies.</p><p>Our IT Apprenticeship programmes are designed to help us attract the brightest and the best from the local community.</p><p>Our\r\n Advanced Apprenticeship programmes offer full-time employment which \r\nbegins with a 12-month programme that combines day-release study and \r\non-the-job training.Our Higher Apprenticeship programme is \r\nrecruiting its next generation of software engineers, with a training \r\nprogramme that culminates in a BSc in Computing and IT Practice.</p>\r\n','apprentices.careers.uk@capgemini.com','',1,'http://www.uk.capgemini.com/capgemini-careers/apprenticeship-programme/apprenticeship-programme-overview/',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 11:05:13','2012-11-15 13:00:27'),(6,'Virgin Media','VirginMedia_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>Virgin Media is the first provider of all four broadband,\r\nTV, mobile phone and home phone services in the UK.</p><p>The company delivers ultrafast broadband connections to over\r\nhalf of all UK homes, with speeds of up to 100Mb, and is expanding this cable\r\nnetwork – the result of a multi-billion pound investment – to reach thousands\r\nmore people across the country.</p><p>Virgin Media has developed the most advanced interactive\r\ntelevision service, bringing together broadcast TV, thousands of hours of on\r\ndemand programming and the best of the web in a single set-top box powered by\r\nTiVo. The company was the first to offer HD TV and 3D on demand to millions of\r\nUK households.</p><p>Virgin Media also operates the most popular virtual mobile\r\nnetwork in the UK which, when launched, was the world’s first such mobile phone\r\nservice. It is also one of the largest fixed-line home phone providers in the\r\ncountry.</p><p>Virgin Media Inc. is listed on the NASDAQ Stock Market and\r\nthe London Stock Exchange (VMED).</p>\r\n','','',1,'http://www.virginmedia.com/careers',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 11:16:06','2012-11-15 13:00:58'),(7,'YH Training','YHTraining_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>At YH Training Services, we’ve had over 25 years experience\r\nof providing Apprenticeships and assisting young people in gaining\r\nApprenticeship employment. In the past 12 months alone we have helped over 500\r\nyoung people in Yorkshire and Humberside gain employment and provided a Level 2\r\nqualification in their chosen field. Some of these apprentices have now\r\nprogressed onto a Level 3 qualification and have had an increase in pay to\r\nreflect this.</p><p>If you’re looking to undertake an Apprenticeship in the\r\nfollowing:</p><ul><li>AAT Accountancy</li><li>Business administration</li><li>Customer service</li><li>ITQ IT User</li><li>Performing manufacturing operations</li><li>Retail</li><li>Warehousing and storage</li></ul><p>then contact us today</p><p>Freephone 0800 542 2848</p><p>Text APP to 07904 598 688</p><p>Or visit our website</p>\r\n','','08005422848',1,'http://www.yh-group.co.uk',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 11:20:18','2012-11-13 11:21:54'),(8,'Lovell Partnership','Lovell_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>For over 30 years Lovell has been working with local\r\nauthorities and housing associations, helping communities rebuild their\r\nidentities with confidence and pride. Lovell was already an industry leader but\r\nhas further increased the size and scope of its operations with the recent\r\nagreement to take on a number of significant contracts from Connaught. We are\r\nable to draw on wide experience, great expertise and unrivalled economies of\r\nscale. We benefit from the backing of the Morgan Sindall Group plc, which turns\r\nover £2.2 billion. But we never forget that behind the numbers are individuals\r\n– residents, tenants, owners, employees - and that their continued satisfaction\r\nis our continued success.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','',1,'http://www.lovell.co.uk/careers',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 11:29:02','2012-11-13 11:29:02'),(9,'National Grid','NationalGrid_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>National Grid is the largest utility business in the UK, and\r\nthe second largest in the United States, our ambition is to grow even more, and\r\nto grow our people in the process.</p><p>The scale of our activities is huge. We own and maintain the\r\n‘grid’ of towers (pylons) and gas pipelines which carries energy across\r\nBritain, and are responsible for all electricity transmission in England and\r\nWales – as well as for Great Britain’s gas transmission in its entirety. We\r\nalso own and manage four of the country’s eight regional gas distribution\r\nnetworks. Though our work is vital to millions of people and industry, we don’t\r\ngenerate energy or supply it direct. Instead, we transport it, making it\r\navailable to energy retailers.</p><p>We offer an attractive starting salary and first-class\r\ntraining and development opportunities. Benefits include generous holidays,\r\npension and share scheme and a popular flexible benefits package.</p>\r\n','','',10,'http://www.nationalgridcareers.com ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 11:34:50','2012-11-15 13:01:34'),(10,'Royal Navy','RoyalNavy_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>ROYAL NAVY – SKILLS FOR LIFE</p><p>Travel, adventure, friendship, challenge, knowing you’re\r\ndoing something really worthwhile – a career with the Royal Navy offers you\r\nmore than any job you’ll find in civilian life. We offer a wide range of\r\nemployment opportunities, but whatever job you choose you’ll begin your career\r\non one of our Apprenticeship schemes.</p><p>The Royal Navy is one of the UK’s largest training\r\norganisations. Training starts the day you join and lasts right through your\r\ntime with us. We fund all our Apprenticeships fully, so you won’t have to pay\r\nany tuition fees. They’re also accredited by civilian organisations, which\r\nmeans they’ll be recognised and valued by any future employers.\r\n</p>','','08456075555',1,'http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/careers',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 11:38:50','2012-11-13 11:39:45'),(11,'Charnwood Training','Charnwood_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>Pubs, restaurants or hotels; customer-facing or behind the\r\nscenes – a career in hospitality is fun, rewarding and can be well paid. No\r\nsitting behind a desk all day, and you could be your own boss within a few\r\nyears!</p><p>An Apprenticeship is the best place to start.</p><p>Charnwood is the fastest-growing provider of Apprenticeships\r\nin the licensed hospitality industry and we’re growing because we’re good at\r\nwhat we do.</p><p>We work with some of the top employers in England and they\r\nhave vacancies waiting for you now!</p><p>If you’re interested in an Apprenticeship in hospitality and\r\nwould like more information please contact us.\r\n</p>','learn@charnwood.co.uk','07970230110',1,'https://www.facebook.com/charn.wood.5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 11:45:17','2012-11-13 11:53:54'),(12,'TTE Technical Training Group','TTE_NEW_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>TTE – Training for Industry</b></p><p>If you want to learn a trade and have a career in industry,\r\nTTE is the place to start!</p><p>We are the UK’s leading technical training provider and we\r\nare based here, in the North East of England.</p><p>We are different from most colleges and other training\r\nproviders because we are specialists. We only do training for industry.</p><p>We have strong links with over 200 local employers in the\r\noil and gas, process, manufacturing and engineering industries and we have\r\nspecialist technical equipment, facilities and expertise that are just not\r\navailable elsewhere.</p><p>Find out more about our great range of Apprenticeship and\r\nPathway courses by visiting our website.</p>\r\n','','01642462266',1,'http://www.tte.co.uk',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 12:01:02','2012-11-15 13:01:15'),(13,'Newton Rigg','NewtonRigg_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>Newton Rigg College is situated in the beautiful Cumbrian\r\ncountryside and is well renowned for offering excellent land-based education.</p><p>At Newton Rigg College we offer Further Education courses\r\nfrom entry level courses up to Level 3 diplomas along with offering a large\r\nvariety of Apprenticeships and Advanced Level Apprenticeships. We offer courses\r\nin Agriculture, Countryside and Land Management, Game Keeping, Animal\r\nManagement, Outdoor Adventure, Engineering, Equine, Forestry and Horticulture.\r\nStudents studying at Newton Rigg College have access to an exceptional range of\r\nfacilities including the National Forestry Training Centre, Northern School of\r\nGame and Wildlife and The Animal Academy. Accommodation is also available on\r\ncampus and our lively student union ensures our students enjoy every minute of\r\ntheir time at College.</p>\r\n','','01768893400',1,'http://www.newtonrigg.ac.uk',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 12:09:13','2012-11-13 12:09:13'),(14,'Doncaster College','Doncaster_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>Doncaster College is a large provider of further education\r\nin South Yorkshire. It is also one of the largest providers of higher education\r\nin this region.</p><p>There are two main campuses – The Hub and its sister campus\r\nat High Melton. The University Centre Doncaster is based at High Melton.</p><p>The Hub campus is situated on the Waterfront in the centre\r\nof Doncaster and is home to some excellent educational facilities. These\r\ninclude state-of-the-art IT facilities, a 100-seat lecture theatre, a 200-seat\r\ndrama studio, a huge two-floor Learning Resource Centre and a beauty salon\r\nwhich is open to the public.</p>\r\n','','',1,'http://www.don.ac.uk/courses/apprenticeships/about_apprenticeships.aspx',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 12:31:56','2012-11-15 13:01:53'),(15,'Askham Bryan College','AskhamBryan_Logo.png',NULL,'<p>We’re proud to be the fastest-growing land-based college in\r\nthe country, thanks to our range of existing courses, great teaching and\r\nfantastic facilities.</p><p>We have courses to suit just about everyone, whether you are\r\nlooking for an entry-level starter course, an honours degree, work-based\r\nlearning or anything in between.</p><p>Our residential campus is near York. We have centres at\r\nBedale, Guisborough (courses up to degree level), Harrogate and Thirsk, and we\r\nalso deliver animal management courses at Bradford, Middlesbrough, Scarborough\r\nand Wakefield. We also have also recently acquired Newton Rigg College in\r\nCumbria.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>','','',1,'http://www.askham-bryan.ac.uk',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 12:46:23','2012-11-13 12:46:23'),(16,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>An Apprenticeship in… Manufacturing</b></p><p>The tough climate that manufacturing has faced in recent\r\nyears has served to place added emphasis on the need to boost productivity and\r\ncompetitiveness and is something that is constantly on the agenda of the UK\r\ngovernment. Skilled staff are needed now and will be the industry leaders in\r\nthe future.</p><p>A number of qualifications are available, both\r\nApprenticeships and Advanced Apprenticeships. These include:</p><ul><li>Performing engineering operations – NVQ Level 2</li><li>Business improvement techniques (BIT) – Vocationally\r\nRelated Qualification (VQR)</li><li>Full Apprenticeship frameworks across a selection of\r\nengineering area</li></ul>\r\n','training@babcock.co.uk','08007318199',1,'http://www.babcock.co.uk/training',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 12:59:07','2012-11-13 12:59:07'),(17,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>An Apprenticeship in… Hospitality</b></p><p>The hospitality industry is probably the world’s\r\nfastest-growing job-creating sector, employing over 1.8 million people in the\r\nUK alone, with enormous scope for career progression.</p><p>Babcock offers Apprenticeships and Advanced Apprenticeships\r\nin Hospitality, which are a great way to start your career, getting qualified\r\nin the workplace while earning a wage. Promotion can come at a younger age than\r\nin other industries, and those with good qualifications are best placed to capitalise\r\non the huge range of opportunities.</p><p>Babcock Hospitality Apprenticeships and Advanced\r\nApprenticeships include:</p><ul><li>HousekeepingFood &amp; drink service</li><li><span></span>Front office</li><li><span></span>Professional cookery</li><li><span></span>Multi-skilled hospitality services<span></span></li><li>Food processing &amp; cooking</li><li><span></span>Hospitality supervision</li></ul>\r\n','training@babcock.co.uk','08007318199 ',1,'http://www.babcock.co.uk/training',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 13:01:46','2012-11-13 13:01:46'),(18,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>An Apprenticeship in… Engineering</b></p><p>Engineering is recognised by the Government as a key area of\r\ngrowth and an industry that requires skilled qualified people now and as\r\nindustry leaders in the future.</p><p>Babcock has a record in the world’s engineering industry\r\nthat stretches back over 150 years. Our apprentices undergo their training in\r\nmany of the UK’s leading engineering businesses including Network Rail, EDF\r\nEnergy Southern Water and BAE Systems.</p><p>An Apprenticeship and Advanced Apprenticeship with Babcock\r\nis a brilliant start to an engineering career, with our exceptional facilities\r\nand specialist staff. Get the very best training together with work experience\r\nand be paid a wage while you’re doing it.</p>','training@babcock.co.uk','08007318199',1,'http://www.babcock.co.uk/training',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 13:04:17','2012-11-13 13:04:17'),(19,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>An Apprenticeship in… Customer Service</b></p><p>The way companies communicate with customers determines:</p><ul><li>How effectively customer enquiries are handled</li><li>How efficiently complaints and problems are resolved<span></span></li><li>How well information and advice is provided<span></span></li><li>Whether a sale is made or not</li></ul><p>Customer Service Apprenticeships are recognised throughout\r\nbusiness and industry as essential ingredients for success. Babcock works with\r\nthe best companies, those wanting to maximise customer service by providing\r\ntheir customer-facing staff with the appropriate training and qualifications.</p><p>An Apprenticeship and Advanced Apprenticeship with Babcock\r\ncan get you started in a world with a huge range of business types. There are\r\nhundreds of different service industries, so the choices are as wide as your\r\nimagination and ambition.</p>\r\n','training@babcock.co.uk','08007318199',1,'http://www.babcock.co.uk/training',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 13:07:04','2012-11-13 13:07:04'),(20,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>An Apprenticeship in… Care</b></p><p>Health and Social Care and Children’s Care, Learning and\r\nDevelopment are both central to the health and well-being of individuals and\r\nfamilies across the UK. Both sectors face significant growth and change, with\r\nemployers seeking to attract committed, motivated and flexible individuals.</p><p>Careers in care can be rewarding and, although child care\r\nand adult care are very different, both require individuals that have patience\r\nand understanding, along with a strong desire to help others.</p><p>Babcock offers Apprenticeships and Advanced Apprenticeships\r\nin both these career paths and these are a great way to start your career,\r\ngetting qualified in the workplace while earning a wage.</p>\r\n','training@babcock.co.uk','08007318199',1,'http://www.babcock.co.uk/training',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 13:08:28','2012-11-13 13:08:28'),(21,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>An Apprenticeship in… Business Administration</b></p><p>The world of business administration has changed\r\ndramatically over the last decade. Advances in technology and regulations mean\r\nthat administrative staff must be kept up-to-date with changing office\r\nprocesses in order to maximise the service that they provide both internally\r\nand to their company\'s clients. This growing sector is now recognised as the\r\nlifeblood of an organisation and roles within the sector are evolving, with\r\ncareer paths to management and senior roles.</p><p>An Apprenticeship and Advanced Apprenticeship with Babcock\r\ncan get you started in a world with a huge range of business types. Every\r\nbusiness has an administrative aspect, so the choices are as wide as your\r\nimagination and ambition.</p>\r\n','training@babcock.co.uk','08007318199',1,'http://www.babcock.co.uk/training',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 13:09:44','2012-11-13 13:09:44'),(22,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>An Apprenticeship in… Automotive</b></p><p>Working in the automotive industry is no longer all about\r\noily overalls and backstreet garages. Much of the work on today’s precision\r\nvehicles is based around computer diagnostics and the industry requires highly\r\nskilled and qualified people. Some things don’t change though – you’ll need\r\nenthusiasm to learn and a passion for cars.</p><p>Babcock offers Apprenticeships and Advanced Apprenticeships\r\nwith some of the biggest names in the industry, including Volkswagen Group,\r\nFerrari, BMW, Hyundai, Fiat, Mazda, Subaru, Chrysler, Isuzu, MINI, and John\r\nDeere as well as the best of local independent dealers.</p><p>Apprenticeships and Advanced Apprenticeship include:</p><ul><li>Service Technician</li><li>Vehicle Body Technician</li><li>Vehicle Paint Technician</li><li><span></span>Parts Consultan </li></ul>\r\n','automotive@babcock.co.uk','08700130325',1,'www.babcock.co.uk/automotivetraining',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 13:13:07','2012-11-13 13:45:07'),(23,'Babcock International','Babcock_Logo.png',NULL,'<b>An Apprenticeship in… Active Leisure</b><br>The UK active leisure industry is a young, dynamic and\r\nthriving business sector which has evolved rapidly in its short history. The\r\ndiversity of the sector means that it contains a vast range of occupations:\r\neverything from personal trainers to activity leaders, and play assistants to\r\nleisure centre managers.<br>With the Olympics 2012 and the Olympic legacy there will be\r\nmore opportunities and focus on this growing sector than ever before.<br>Babcock offers Apprenticeships and Advanced Apprenticeships\r\nin Active Leisure, which are a great way to start your career, getting\r\nqualified in the workplace while earning a wage.\r\n','training@babcock.co.uk','08007318199',1,'http://www.babcock.co.uk/training',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-13 13:14:42','2012-11-13 13:14:42'),(25,'British Institute of Inkeeping (BII)','BII_logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>BII Apprenticeship in Licensed Hospitality</b></p>\r\n<p>BII is now offering the first Apprenticeship programme in\r\nLicensed Hospitality, designed for staff working or wishing to work in licensed\r\npremises such as pubs, clubs, hotels and restaurants.</p>\r\n<p>As an Apprentice in Licensed Hospitality you can:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>learn and develop your skills through hands-on experience in\r\nthe workplace, while earning a wage</li><li>receive an award acknowledged across industry and in wider\r\nworkforce training</li><li>receive one year’s complimentary BII foundation membership</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you’re starting your career or already working in a\r\nlicensed retail outlet and would like to develop your long-term career\r\nprospects, then an Apprenticeship in Licensed Hospitality could be the option\r\nfor you.</p>','apprenticeships@bii.org','01276684449',1,'http://www.biiab.org/apprenticeships',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-29 14:38:51','2012-11-29 15:02:45'),(26,'British Sugar','BritishSugar_logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>British Sugar Apprenticeship Scheme</b></p>\r\n<p>If you would rather earn while you learn, with a mixture of\r\non-the-job training at our factories and college study, and a valuable\r\nqualification or two at the end of it all, our apprenticeship scheme could be\r\nright up your street.</p>','graduate.recruitment@britishsugar.com','01733422398',1,'http://www.notjustsugar.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-29 14:45:29','2012-11-29 15:03:07'),(27,'Sport Structures','SportStructures_logo.png',NULL,'<p>Sport Structures are an established training provider based\r\nin the West Midlands. We are national providers for coach education for a range\r\nof governing bodies and we are now providing Apprenticeships at Intermediate\r\nand Advanced level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apprentices work towards work-based learning qualifications,\r\nfunctional skills and, in most cases, a relevant knowledge-based qualification.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a 1st4sport Approved Centre and deliver a 1st4sport\r\nframework of qualifications for the following Apprenticeship programmes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Sports Coaching</b>\r\n(Intermediate Activity Leadership Apprenticeship) – Coaching pathway</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>PE &amp; School Sport</b>\r\n(Intermediate Activity Leadership Apprenticeship) – Leadership pathway</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Sports Development</b> (Advanced\r\nApprenticeship)</p>\r\n','amy@sportstructures.com','08452417195',1,'http://www.sportstructures.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-29 14:52:55','2012-11-29 15:03:44'),(28,'Leeds College of Building','LeedsCollegeofBuilding_Logo.png',NULL,'<p><b>Construction – a career that’s going places!</b></p>\r\n<p>At Leeds College of Building (LCB) we specialise in\r\nConstruction Education and Training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Construction is the creation of the built environment around\r\nus, from repair and maintenance, to housing developments, to sporting stadiums.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is an interesting and rewarding career path, you can earn\r\nwhile you learn, be your own boss and manage high-profile projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are hundreds of job roles, from site work to office\r\nwork or a combination of the two.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Getting into construction is easy and at LCB we have a\r\nnumber of routes, from Apprenticeships to vocational qualifications and\r\nacademic courses.</p>\r\n<p></p>','info@lcb.ac.uk','01132226002',1,'http://www.lcb.ac.uk',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-29 14:54:42','2012-11-29 15:04:04'),(29,'ICAEW','ICAEW_logo.png',NULL,'\r\n<p>The Institute of Chartered Accountants in England and Wales\r\n(ICAEW) is a professional membership organisation that promotes, supports and\r\nregulates over 138,000 ICAEW Chartered Accountants around the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You need to complete the ACA qualification to become an\r\nICAEW Chartered Accountant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A growing number of organisations now offer the opportunity\r\nto train for the ACA qualification straight after A-levels (or equivalent).\r\nSchool leaver programmes vary but typically it takes 3–5 years to complete. You\r\ncould be a fully qualified ICAEW Chartered Accountant by the time you’re 21.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most organisations will ask you to prepare for the ACA\r\nqualification by completing one of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul><li>ICAEW Certificate in Finance, Accounting and Business</li><li>Higher Apprenticeship in Assurance/Audit</li><li>Association of Accounting Technicians qualification (AAT)</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p></p>','careers@icaew.com','01908248050',10,'http://careers.icaew.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-29 15:00:37','2012-11-29 15:00:37');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `employers` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

